responseRequest.instructions:
I understand that I am entitled to a rest period of 10 minutes net rest for each 4 hours of work or major fraction thereof and the rest periods should occur in the middle of each work period insofar as practicable.  This means that I am entitled to two 10-minute rest periods for an eigh-hour shift.  In addition, I understand that I am entitled to a meal period of at least 30 minutes if I work more than five hours in a day.

Adding some more text to make this even longer so that we can add scrolling to the text box and then still be able to utilize the left to right scrolling as well as Approve the timecard.
